---------------->"VI EDITOR COMMANDS"

1. yy --> copy, nyy -->copy n lines
2. p -->paste
3. x -> delete single character
4. dd -->delete current line
5. nx --> delete n characters
6. Cursor Movement:
    j->down
    k->up
    h->left
    l->right

